ar Allah, pray your prayers, obey your leaders","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said in his farewell sermon, \u201cFear Allah your Lord, pray your five prayers, fast your month of Ramadan, give charity from your wealth, and obey those in authority over you. You will enter the Paradise of your Lord.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5171,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/15\/trial-of-ummah-wealth\/","url_meta":{"origin":19373,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Trial of the Muslim nation is its wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn 'Iyad reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, every nation has a trial, and the trial of my nation is wealth.\u201d Source:\u00a0Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2336 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0636\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u00a0\u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0644\u0650\u0643\u064f\u0644\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9953,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/24\/best-honor-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":19373,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Honor: Best in honor are best in character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn al-'Asim reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhat do you consider nobility? Allah has made clear the most noble to Allah is the most righteous. What do you consider honor? The best in honor are those among you with the best character.\u201d Source: al-Adab\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18059,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/05\/merchants-wicked-unless-fear-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19373,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Trade: Merchants with the wicked, unless they fear Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa\u2019ah ibn Rafi' reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him,\u00a0said, \u201cVerily, merchants will be raised on the Day of Resurrection with the wicked, except for those who fear Allah, behave righteously, and are truthful.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1210 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u0650\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0639\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0646 \u0631\u0627\u0641\u0639\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1972,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/17\/akhlaq-fear-allah-wherever\/","url_meta":{"origin":19373,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Fear Allah everywhere, have good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFear\u00a0Allah wherever you are, follow a bad deed with a good deed and it will erase it, and behave with good character towards people.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1987 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19203,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/19\/world-four-kinds-of-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":19373,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Knowledge: Worldly life only has four types of people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Kabshah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the world only has four kinds of people. There is one whom Allah has granted wealth and knowledge, so he fears his Lord in them, upholds family ties, and fulfills the rights of Allah over\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hi